/* GH #124 Phase 2b: pins the positional field indices of every IfcRel*
   the subset pass understands. One record per rule; anchor refs use the
   #50xx band, pull refs the #40xx band, so tests/doc_rel_rules.rs can
   assert exact anchor/pull extraction. Field layouts match real records
   (IfcRelDefinesByType / IfcRelVoidsElement / IfcRelAssignsToGroup were
   cross-checked against ifc-art + ST28_RIB corpus output). Referenced
   ids are intentionally dangling: this fixture pins field POSITIONS, not
   graph validity. */
